<h2>Sensor Control Template</h2>
<div style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;"><img src="/assets/img/sensor-control.webp" alt="Sensor Control" style="width: 60%; height: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto;"></div>

<p>The Sensor Control template provides a flexible foundation for building devices that monitor and respond to environmental conditions using Ultiblocks' modular components. Supporting a wide range of sensors, displays, and output types, this template adapts to numerous use cases, enabling responsive control and feedback.</p>

<h3>Compatible Components</h3>

<h4><a href="/components/sensors">Sensors</a></h4>
<p>Integrate various sensors, including temperature, moisture, and light sensors, to monitor and react to environmental data in real-time.</p>

<h4><a href="/components/displays">Displays</a></h4>
<p>Choose from multiple display types, such as OLED and LCD, to visualize data directly on the device, enhancing feedback and interactivity.</p>

<h4><a href="/components/outputs">Output Controls</a></h4>
<p>Utilize MOSFETs and relays to control power-driven components, enabling automation based on sensor readings for applications like switching motors or lights.</p>

<h3>Applications</h3>
<ul style="padding-left: 20px; list-style-type: disc;">
  <li><strong>Automated Plant Care:</strong> Adjusts watering based on soil moisture levels.</li>
  <li><strong>Temperature-Based Fan Control:</strong> Activates a fan when temperatures exceed a set point.</li>
  <li><strong>Ambient Lighting:</strong> Adjusts lighting based on ambient light levels for energy efficiency.</li>
</ul>
